<div type="definition">
<p>COMMON BELIEF that is NOT BASED on REALITY.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
<p>謠言 is the current modern word for a rumour.</p>
<p>謠傳 focusses on the oral transmission of rumours.</p>
<p>妄言 focusses on the misleadingness of rumours.</p>
<p>無稽之談 (prov) focusses on the baselessness of rumours.</p>
<p>黃色新聞 (prov) refers to lurid published rumours.</p>
<p>桃色新聞 (prov) refers to lurid published rumours.</p>
<p>謠 (cl)</p>
<p>rough draft to BEGIN TO identify synonym group members for analysis, based on CL etc. 18.11.2003. CH ／</p>
        </div>
